                <button class="quiz-option" data-correct="true">
                    Built-in email confirmation and password reset
                </button>
                <button class="quiz-option" data-correct="false">
                    A system you need to code from scratch
                </button>
            </div>
            
            <div class="quiz-feedback">
                <p id="quiz-feedback-text"></p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="key-takeaway">
        <h3>The Bottom Line</h3>
        <div class="takeaway-content">
            <p><strong>.NET's "Individual Accounts" authentication gives you a professional, secure authentication system without writing authentication code.</strong></p>
            <p>You don't need to be a security expert. You don't need to implement cryptographic algorithms. You don't need to build user management from scratch.</p>
            <p>Just select "Individual Accounts" when creating your project, and you get a battle-tested authentication system that's used by thousands of applications worldwide.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

